field.value:
Let the code speak:

{code lang=java}
public class ExtensibleBehavior : IEndpointBehavior, IExtensibleObject<ExtensibleBehavior>
{
	// impl
}

public class ExtensibleBehaviorExtension : IExtension<ExtensibleBehavior>
{
	public ExtensibleBehaviorExtension()
	{
	}

	public ExtensibleBehaviorExtension(ExtensibleBehavior behavior)
	{
	}
	// impl
}
{code}

This scenario will cause a Stack Overflow because Windsor will not detect the cycle.
